<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v2" title="Q28_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un laboratorio se estudia la descarga de la batería de un dispositivo electrónico. Se sabe que esta batería se descarga a rapidez constante.</p>
    <p>Esta rapidez <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>, medida en miliamperios-hora por hora (<m:math><m:mtext>mAh/h</m:mtext></m:math>), se modela con la expresión <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>, donde <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi></m:math> es la carga consumida, en mAh, y <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es el tiempo, en horas, hasta que esa carga se consume completamente.</p>
    <p>En una prueba se programa el dispositivo para consumir <m:math><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mtext> mAh</m:mtext></m:math> de carga con una rapidez de <m:math><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mtext> mAh/h</m:mtext></m:math>. Según este modelo, ¿cuánto tiempo dura la prueba de descarga? Da tu respuesta en minutos.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">40 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mtext> min</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mtext> h</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mtext> h</m:mtext></m:math>. Con esa duración, la carga consumida sería <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3200</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> mAh, que no es 2400 mAh.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">60 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mtext> min</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> h</m:mtext></m:math>. Con esa duración, la carga consumida sería <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn></m:math> mAh, que no es 2400 mAh.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">90 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! De <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math> se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mn>1600</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mtext> h</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mtext> h</m:mtext></m:math>. En minutos, <m:math><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:math> minutos.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">150 minutos<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mtext> min</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mn>60</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mtext> h</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mtext> h</m:mtext></m:math>. Con esa duración, la carga consumida sería <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2,5</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:math> mAh, que no es 2400 mAh.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la fórmula del modelo</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado indica que la rapidez de descarga se modela por <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como se conoce la carga consumida <m:math><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mtext> mAh</m:mtext></m:math> y la rapidez <m:math><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mtext> mAh/h</m:mtext></m:math>, debemos despejar el tiempo <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Despejar el tiempo</strong></p>
            <p>De <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>, multiplicando por <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> y luego dividiendo por <m:math><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reemplazar los valores</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mn>1600</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mtext> h</m:mtext></m:math></p>
            <p>Simplificando la fracción:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2400</m:mn><m:mn>1600</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1,5</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, la duración es <m:math><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mtext> h</m:mtext></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Convertir horas a minutos</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> h</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mtext> min</m:mtext></m:math>, se tiene:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>1,5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>La prueba dura <m:math><m:mn>90</m:mn><m:mtext> minutos</m:mtext></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>C</strong>: 90 minutos.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>